divs: Sighting DetailsMe and a few of my friend were walking back in the woods when we kept hearing a rustling sound coming from the northern part of the deep woods and we shown our flashlights on it and the grey short figure poped its head up and ran north east to a deep section of the woods, we chased it but couldnt catch it, so we went back home in awe of what had happened
Summary: Grey human like entity in woods
